N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 22.95 - Liquidation

State Regulations

Upon the termination or suspension of this Part, the
commissioner shall dispose in an equitable manner of all funds received
pursuant to the provisions of this Part, together with claims for any funds
which are unpaid and owing at the time of such termination or
suspension. Notes
